            <title>[LU-14088] sanity/60a remounts MDS w/o local recovery</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14088</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when sanity is running on a local setup and MGS is shared with MDS, then remounting MGS causes MDS to lose local_recov mountoption. then any test can randomly fail as any client reconnection results in a client eviction.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
